Shortcuts in window  

search storage       --> clearing temp 
search mrt           --> window antivirus
search nightlight    --> night mode
search step recorder --> to see step what i do 
window + shift + s   --> screen shot 
window + + --> magnifier
window + g --> screen recorder
window + w --> white board
window + e --> file explore
window + r --> run 
window + D --> desktop
window + p --> change screen (dual or one monitor)
window + a --> side tab 
window + h --> voice typeing 
window + k --> connect bluetooth device
window + x --> window feature 
window + v --> copy / paste
window + m --> miinimise all window 
window + . --> emoji 
window + t --> task bar access
window + number  --> acces taksbar icons
fn + arrow       --> keyword light
fn + v           --> fps/deaflat/rfg
alt + tab        --> switch tabs
win + shift + d  --> new desktop 
win + shit + arrow  --> return page
window + space   --> change laguages






